    "description": "GRCS Inc. engages in security-related solutions business in Japan. The company offers Enterprise Risk MT, an ERM tool that provides company-wide risk management; Supplier Risk MT, a cloud application that streamlines external contractor management and business partner management; OneTrust, a data privacy solution; Simple R, which links the learning management and ID management systems; and Connected Risk GRC Solution Audit Module, an audit management cloud solution. It also provides CSIRT MT.mss, an integrated security risk management tool; Vulnerability TODAY, an email distribution service that collect vulnerability information; Netskope, a cloud security platform that utilizes secure access service edge; HENNGE ONE, a SaaS authentication platform that provides secure access to cloud services and single sign-on functionality; HP Sure Click Enterprise; SecureCube Access Check; Imperva App Protect; Internal Risk Intelligence; Privilege Management for Windows; RidgeBot; GOOSEC; and SOCRadar, an extended threat intelligence. In addition, the company offers enterprise risk management advanced support consulting and training, management system operation improvement, sustainability support, and robotic process automation; and security services, such as cloud security measures, security product implementation and operation support, PCI DSS compliance support solution, AI-generated security risk management support, security support, compliant security support solution, penetration testing, physical penetration testing, AI-powered service risk assessment, purple team training, ransomware incident preparedness assessment, voice fishing training, and security measures evaluation system compliance support services. The company was formerly known as NANAROQ Inc. and changed its name to GRCS Inc. in May 2018. GRCS Inc. was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Chiyoda, Japan."
